### Prize Assignments — Configure weekly/monthly prizes for each rank

### List prize assignments for my family
GET {{host}}/api/prize-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Set (upsert) a prize assignment (admin only)
### scope: Week | Month   rank: 1 | 2 | 3  (rank 2 and 3 are weekly only)
PUT {{host}}/api/prize-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "Week",
  "rank": 1,
  "emoji": "🍦",
  "label": "Ice cream"
}

###

### Set 2nd place weekly prize
PUT {{host}}/api/prize-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "Week",
  "rank": 2,
  "emoji": "🎬",
  "label": "Movie night"
}

###

### Set 3rd place weekly prize
PUT {{host}}/api/prize-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "Week",
  "rank": 3,
  "emoji": "🌙",
  "label": "Late bedtime"
}

###

### Set monthly grand prize
PUT {{host}}/api/prize-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "Month",
  "rank": 1,
  "emoji": "🎡",
  "label": "Amusement park"
}
